profile: Anchor Self Storage is committed to providing a clean, secure, affordable, and locally owned Self Storage Facility, staffed by knowledgeable and pleasant individuals to ensure their customers' Peace of Mind.  Anchor Self Storage Units are impeccably clean, always kept dry and pest controlled.  We are an Authorized U-Haul Dealer offering Truck and Trailer Rentals.  We Sell Boxes and also offer Moving & Packing Supplies at the onsite Retail Store for a One-Stop Shopping Experience.  Anchor Self Storage is a Fully Fenced Property and its Electronic Gate System allows PIN Access to tenants' belongings 24 Hours per Day, 7 Days a Week.  What sets Anchor Self Storage apart is their exceptional customer service and superior storage solutions.
